                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donors; 1st, 2nd, 6th, 7th, 13th and 14th line on the incipit page of Text I; two initial lines of parts of Text II; a few lines of the beginning of the daily readings and their sections in Text I; the words sälam läki, sǝḥat läkä and their abbreviations in Text II; elements of punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals. &#xD;
